TextEng: What seems to be the trouble?
What wrong?
I've no time for this. Goodbye.
Me not have time. Bye.
Who was this man?
Who the man?
You paid with an amulet?
You pay with neck thing?
I suppose I could look into it for you.
Text: 알아봐 줄 수 있을 것 같은데.

TextEng: Maybe me look into it.
How valuable is "valuable?"
How valuable you mean?
Masterson? I believe I have an amulet of yours.
Text: 마스터슨? 당신 호신부를 가지고 있는 것 같은데.

TextEng: You Masterson? Me have your amulet.
Text: 너 마스터슨? 나 너 호신부 가지고 있어.

TextEng: What do you know about the docks?
Text: 항만 지구에 대해 아는 게 있나요?

TextEng: What you know about docks?
I have your amulet here.
Me find your amulet.
I'll see what I can do.
Maybe me find it. Me look.
I need you to repeat some things.
You maybe repeat some things?
Here you go. I am pleased to return it.
Text: 여기 있어. 돌려드릴 수 있어서 기뻐.

TextEng: Take it. Me glad to give it back.
I'd like a reward for returning it.
Text: 돌려주는 것에 대한 보상을 받고 싶어.

TextEng: Me want reward for giving it back.
Now, let's talk about adequate payment, fool.
Text: 자, 적절한 대가에 대해 이야기해 보자고, 멍청아.

TextEng: Now we talk payment. Big payment.
Actually, I think I'll keep it.
Maybe me just keep it.
That will be fine. Thank you.
That good enough.
I want more. Don't make me angry.
Text: 더 원해. 날 화나게 하지 마.

TextEng: You give more or me get violent!
Text: 너 더 줘, 안 그러면 나 폭력적으로 변할 거야!

TextEng: Me worth more, don't you think?
Text: 나 더 가치 있잖아, 그렇게 생각 안 해?

TextEng: You must agree I am worth more?
Text: 내가 더 가치 있다는 데 동의하지 않아?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Come now, you know I'll use it well.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 자, 내가 잘 쓸 거라는 거 알잖아.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You know me use it good. Come on.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 잘 쓸 거 알아. 좋지?

TextEng: Give it to me or die! I won't ask again!
Text: 내놔, 아니면 죽는다! 두 번 말하지 않겠다!

TextEng: Give me the amulet or me hurt you! Now!
Text: 목걸이 내놔, 아니면 다치게 한다! 지금!

TextEng: I meant no harm. I'll leave.
Me not want to scare. Me leave.
I won't help for free.
Me not help for free.
I've no interest in helping you.
Me not care. No want to help yous.
Text: 나 신경 안 써. 너 돕고 싶지 않아.
